Package: textmineR
Title: Functions for topic modeling and other text mining
Version: 1.1
Date: 2015-04-14
Authors: "Thomas W. Jones <jones.thos.w@gmail.com>"
Maintainer: Thomas W. Jones <jones.thos.w@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements various functions related to 
    latent Dirichlet allocation (LDA). It is designed to work with
		the "lda" package by J. Chang. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1),
    lda,
    snowfall,
    wordcloud,
    Matrix,
    slam,
    RcppArmadillo,
    tm,
    RWeka,
    SnowballC
License: LGPL
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    reshape2,
    ggplot2 (>= 0.9.1),
    penalized
LinkingTo: Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppProgress
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppProgress
